CustomField.description: When True, schedules and schedule exceptions are respected when assignments or resource requests are dragged and dropped in the Project Planner timeline. Non-working time is respected. The default value is False.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: When True, schedules and schedule exceptions are respected when assignments or resource requests are dragged and dropped in the Project Planner timeline. Non-working time is respected. The default value is False.
CustomField.label: Respect Schedules
